Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic put up MVP numbers with 27 points, 16 rebounds, and 9 assists, shooting 56/75/100 from the field, propelling the Nuggets to victory
Pre-Game Insights: Coach Malone thought it might be 5-7 days for Jamal Murray's return due to concussion protocols
Post-Match Reflections: Jamal Murray's teammates stepped up to fill the void he left, making it safer to ease him back from concussion protocols
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Denver Nuggets will take on the Toronto Raptors on November 4 at 10:00 p.m. EST
Others: Jamal Murray has been a pivotal piece in the Nuggets' game plan, but the team still managed to win without him
